Oo?

00:08:21.035 --> 00:08:22.473
Kung hindi ka isang mamamahayag

00:08:22.805 --> 00:08:24.289
Maaari kang magbukas ng isang tea cafe.

00:08:24.321 --> 00:08:25.321
Maganda talaga.

